Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be fine. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you shoot me like you did before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will be the end of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The end…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Many, many times I have seen the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die, and so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you've seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the truly horrifying story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A truly horrifying story, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The stories of the things that I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The many stories…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that I told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After I was dragged from\Nour home at the Three Frogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the place I was taken to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was a pitch-black room with no walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell up from down\Nor right from left in that room,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything I touched felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell that someone was watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The room was completely silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Except occasionally I could hear\Nscreams from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The meals appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I counted the meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Five. Six. Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven. Twelve. Thirteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-one. Twenty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when I'd lost track of the number…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That man appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People can become\Nwhatever they want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:06:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right for a little child\Nlike you to be wandering around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this is the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent! What a beautiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this is the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the child, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What fine results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very good results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us now raise…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I only remember fragments\Nof the speech that was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,…for us, the chosen elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To the future of the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,First, one person collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those around him gathered around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then those who gathered around\Nbegan collapsing on top of one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There were moans, screams, and shouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The room was overflowing with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the 42 lives that were taken that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta was\Nthe only one who remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran to escape from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran without even noticing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that the thorns on the rose bush\Nin the garden had injured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When I arrived at the Three Frogs,\Nyou welcomed me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For days and days…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about everything I experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me, right? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's the way. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There. That's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me who said, "Welcome back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who said that was…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What… I said was…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan only listened to what I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who was taken away\Nto the Red Rose Mansion…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who was taken away\Nto the Red Rose Mansion was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who was dragged away down\Nthe stairs at the Three Frogs…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who counted the meals\Nin the pitch-black room without walls…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who stood there\Nin the room filled with corpses…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,THREE FROGS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For days and days…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Johan what I'd been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan took my experiences and…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan took my experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and made them his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that Johan--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Johan everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When Johan listened to me,\Nhe seemed to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But he also seemed to be crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a human…\Nlook that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't… shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he will destroy himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I will destroy myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what would I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you died, where would I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay alive no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find the car near the villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. It was driven off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward is dead inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely, Johan has…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,gone to kill Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,His son is in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Johan that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that will end things…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or if his destruction\Nwill end at just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The sister's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Something missing from her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan has one other memory in him.\NThat other memory…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly was the thing\Nthat we imagined we were creating…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a place for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there is, somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I'm really glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm usually the one coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just made some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted you\Nto have some of my best tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:20:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?\NIt's my very own special herb tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've come\Nall the way here to visit me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,this must be something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask for anything you like.\NI can be ready in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you want me to kill this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Stop messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've woken…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why the heck\Ndid I collect all that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've woken from the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck did I kill all those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen many scenes at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I can see a different scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the scene of the real end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory that only I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I truly should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The place I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,MR. LIPSKÝ BONAPARTA
